Metadata: Northwest Fish Hatchery Newsletter (Volume 2, Number 1 and Number 2, February and June 1986)
Oregon State University Extension/Sea Grant Program
Two newsletter issues in one entry for 1986.

The following topics are in these issues: Volitional Coho Releases, A. Appleby; Safety First! A Portable GFI!, S. Robart; A New Method for Quick Net Repairs, R.G. Kolb; Oxygen Generator, D. Ewing, and more. Number 2: Fish Quality Assessment, by R. Goede; Lasers and Wizards, by E. Maxwell; The Leaky Boot; Salty Sperm More effective, D. Ewing; Silt causes egg losses, Q. Smith; Volitional release of Steelhead, D. Ewing; Water Quality Strips.
